en_localized_data: “The best games in the world are free!”
en_description_airport_city: Build your very own airport and send hundreds of flights skyward! The time has come to try your hand as a pilot, a flight attendant, and even an air traffic controller. Airport City lets players take off in two exciting modes: the first offers the chance to build and manage a modern airport, while the second lets you build a city to support your international gateway.
